min([u]+[v], [u^{-1}]+[vu^{-1}], [v^{-1}]+[uv^{-1}]) <= p-1.

This is a pure arithmetic statement about F_p. It says: given two "non-antipodal" elements,
at least one of three "inversions" produces a pair summing to at most p-1.

